The Avengers have found out that Thor's home has been destroyed and now they are facing a new enemy,Thanos.
They come together and try to fight Thanos.But he is too powerful and the Avengers have to retreat to save themselves
Now they need to find out what Thanos wants and how to defeat them.

They work with Thor and Dr.Strange to find out what Thanos wants. Thor realises that he is after the infinity stones.
He has already killed Vision for his stone.

Thanos is gathering his army and preparing to attack Wakanda.King T'Challa has been warned and he is also gathering
his allies and preparing for war.